answersResultList.title: True Aries.
answersResultList.resultContent: You're energetic, noisy and uninhibited, and if others can't deal, it's their problem. You get what you want, period. If not, anyone standing in your way is going to be unhappy. As a powerhouse of ambition and creativity, you know what you're worth and will gladly take your services to the highest bidder. Loved ones might have a hard time keeping up with you, but they'll always know where you stand. That's because love is a lot like ownership for you, meaning that friends and family are forever. And you'll fight anyone who tries to tell you different!

answersResultList.title: Somewhat Aries.
answersResultList.resultContent: Why all the questions and second-guessing? A true Aries wouldn't process and weigh the options. No, a true Aries just goes for it. And when you finally do charge ahead, it's with a watery surge instead of a fiery explosion. You can laugh at yourself (always a healthy trait), but if you were a true Aries, your ego would be much closer to the surface. Sometimes you'll push yourself to win the game or close the deal, but other times it just doesn't matter. You could be best friends with an Aries, and you'd both be richer for it.

answersResultList.title: Mostly Aries.
answersResultList.resultContent: Aries leads with the head, and you're big on planning things - same body part, slightly different use. You look good in red, although you'd be just as happy in another attention-getting color. Like a true Aries, it's all about you. Unlike a true Aries, you're more lover than fighter, but only a fool would think of challenging you. You can be just as goal-oriented as the Ram, although you'll easily switch to the path of least resistance when someone else says it's playtime. A true Aries could learn a lot from you about the art of having fun.

answersResultList.resultContent: You're energetic, noisy and uninhibited, and if others can't deal, it's their problem. You get what you want, period. If not, anyone standing in your way is going to be unhappy. As a powerhouse of ambition and creativity, you know what you're worth and will gladly take your services to the highest bidder. Loved ones might have a hard time keeping up with you, but they'll always know where you stand. That's because love is a lot like ownership for you, meaning that friends and family are forever. And you'll fight anyone who tries to tell you different!
